So this is the upload
of the first pass

00:03:33.836 --> 00:03:36.096
where we are rendering
basically through that buffer

00:03:36.096 --> 00:03:38.566
from the perspective of
the directional light.

00:03:39.956 --> 00:03:42.566
And this is how our
