a buffer for each work-group

00:36:43.906 --> 00:36:45.996
so I just want to
allocate one buffer

00:36:46.096 --> 00:36:49.566
so guess what index
would I use to write?

00:36:49.936 --> 00:36:51.176
That would be my work-group ID

00:36:51.176 --> 00:36:54.326
